A bustling workshop classroom in Taipei viewed from behind, showing rows of focused developers hunched over laptops with glowing screens, in the foreground an elegant traditional Asian tea service with multiple ceramic pots steaming gently on a wooden tray, warm amber lighting casting soft shadows, through large windows the Taipei cityscape is visible with modern skyscrapers against misty mountains, the scene blends technology and traditional culture seamlessly, Studio Ghibli animation style with soft watercolor textures, warm earthy tones of jade green, cream, and copper, gentle atmospheric perspective creating depth, whimsical details in the steam rising from the tea pots forming subtle swirling patterns.
